---
title: Teriyaki Mushroom Noodle Stir-Fry with Asian Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: This teriyaki stir-fry is packed with umami-rich mushrooms, slurp-worthy udon noodles, and vibrant Asian greens, all tossed in a glossy ginger-spiked teriyaki glaze. It’s speedy, saucy, and seriously satisfying.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
